          <title>Trump threatens to try to take back the Panama Canal</title>
          <description><![CDATA[PHOENIX (AP) — Donald Trump suggested Sunday that his new administration could try to regain control of the Panama Canal that the United States “foolishly” ceded to its Central American ally, contending that shippers are charged “ridiculous” fees to pass through the vital transportation channel link]]></description>
